{"tid":1469441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不割不只係口號 係要行動做","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:06.000Z","uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8f358599bfe353486488d74c6003d8255a36b5a5","tid":1469441,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"實際就係勇武塞機場 同和理飛割<br />\n <br />\n好簡單一句問題 <br />\n<strong><br />\n你地塞左機場離境 好似好成功咁 塞左機場啵</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁係咪姐係和理飛唔駛出現先?<br />\n<br />\n反正你地人少都做到啦 我地都唔駛出現?</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">問題你係需要和理非既支持 你做既野係會減少參與和理飛既人數? </span></span><br />\n<br />\n人地批評你一句就冷氣軍師 三毛割<br />\n<br />\n到底你割人 定係人地割你<br />\n<br />\n人少咪慢慢等到人多囉<br />\n<br />\n我地無要求 你地咁少人去做到 星期一咁啵<br />\n<br />\n機場24小時運作 你塞左離境 只係唔俾旅客上機 要飛既機一樣飛到<br />\n<br />\n機場既弱點就係交通 唔係旅客<br />\n<br />\n無論貨物同人都好 都係要透過交通入 橋就得一條<br />\n<br />\n你塞離境 只係直接同旅客衝突 你地又要同旅客解釋?浪費幾多時間係無謂既野到? 唔係民意既問題 係令到自己仲多野做<br />\n<br />\n我地係針對政權 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n唔好再講之前 如果你地日後再BLOCK離境 可預見就係全世界會圍屌你 <br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"bb3bc065a5b1934eb4c2b932fff16c108d15ecfd","tid":1469441,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9e3f17fd4976ecc7e76e54ef81396641b172a7","tid":1469441,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6780c1a68d8e39f5be0793635e21d27683116d6","tid":1469441,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28513e52ffffa772915a8de4abbbff636ac13b22","tid":1469441,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91492f8df12fd3c8ea8b36b9de23bb448ca0701d","tid":1469441,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}